        <p>Konark TempleKonark Temple is the most popular and major attraction of Konark in Orissa. Konark is located at an approximate distance of 65 kms from Bhubaneshwar and 35 kms from Puri. [&hellip;]</p>
        <footer><a href="https://www.culturalindia.net/indian-temples/konark-temple.html">Read More</a></footer>
